flowchart TD
    A([上电复位]) --> B[main 入口]
    B --> C[HAL_Init + SystemClock_Config]
    C --> D[MX_GPIO / ADC2 / TIM2 / TIM3 / TIM16 / TIM17 初始化]
    D --> E[app_init]
    E --> F[主循环 while 1]
    F --> G[app_run: key_handle + Lcd_Refresh]
    G --> F

    H[TIM3 1ms 周期中断] -.硬件触发.-> I[timer_task_dispatch]
    J[TIM16 上升沿捕获中断] -.硬件触发.-> K[flow_ic_capture]
